commit.message:
Only accept responses for the most recent age

This should prevent bugs where making too many requests at once causes the
translation to rapidly change before settling on the final response: Now,
it will only render the final response.

Remove always-uppercase display of textareas

Signed-off-by: Ryan Hodin <ryan951357@gmail.com>
